News.headline: Important Vanarama National League Fixture News
News.page_title: Important Vanarama National League Fixture News
News.URL_keywords: Important Vanarama National League Fixture News
News.short_description: The National League have announced that all matches in the Vanarama National League, schedulued for Saturday 29th April will now kick off at 12:15pm
News.description:
All Vanarama National League fixtures for the last game of the 2016/2017 season on Saturday 29th April will now be kicking off at 12:15pm, meaning that the Daggers home fixture against Woking will now be a 12:15pm kick off.

BT Sport will as usual be screening one selected match from the fixture list and covering any other matches which may have a bearing on the League Title, Play Off positions and any possible relegation issues.
